Title: Bosonic Casimir effect in external magnetic field
Authors: M.V. Cougo-Pinto, C. Farina, M. R. Negrao and A. C. Tort
Comments: 9 pages, revised and up dated version
Journal-ref: J.Phys. A32 (1999) 4457-4462
\\
  We compute the influence of an external magnetic field on the Casimir energy
of a massive charged scalar field confined between two parallel infinite
plates. For this case the obtained result shows that the magnetic field
inhibits the Casimir effect.
